text: Anne van Rooijen (born 4 June 2000) is a Dutch professional racing cyclist from Enter, who currently rides since 2022 for UCI Women's Continental Team Parkhotel Valkenburg Cycling Team. Van Rooijen earned a contract with Parkhotel Valkenburg Cycling Team in 2022. She competed during her first year of a professional cyclist at the 2022 Tour de France Femmes. Her two year older sister Sofie van Rooijen is also a professional cyclist, riding for the same team. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch cyclists Category:Sportswomen
